items.title: Lee & Associates sells Phoenix industrial portfolio for $12.45 million
items.summary:
Lee & Associates Arizona announced today that the Koss | Louer team arranged the sale of a 95,836-square-foot industrial portfolio. Luke Marley, LLC., a California-based partnership owning retail product in California, purchased the portfolio from Delcor, LLC. for $12.45 million.
